d on the balancing of karma/karmaphala sequenci=\r\nng of all beings.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;The assignment and ordering of=\r\n these pools will constantly undergo churn as one engages in various new ac=\r\ntions and adds them to the pools. Also, as new people enter one&#39;s life, pos=\r\nsibilities in terms of karmaphala delivery agents\n and sequencing may chang=\r\ne and hence the pools may be re-arranged.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;*&nbsp=\r\n;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=\r\n&nbsp; *&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;As one engages in remedial measures suc=\r\nh as prayers, fasting, donations etc, one may transform one&#39;s nature, chang=\r\ne one&#39;s vulnerabilities or re-arrange one&#39;s dynamics with other beings (inc=\r\nluding planets, deities etc, who are the subtle agents of delivery of karma=\r\nphala, who operate through other people who act as physical agents of deliv=\r\nery!). The karma pools may be re-arranged as a result. Some undesirable kar=\r\nmas may be downgraded to a lower pool or pushed down in order within the sa=\r\nme pool. Or, some desirable karmas may be upgraded to a higher pool or push=\r\ned up in order within the same pool.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;When someone cur=\r\nses or blesses one, with &lt;span style=3D&quot;font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;sufficient &lt;/sp=\r\nan&gt;mental force behind it (this is the key),\n the same thing &lt;span&gt;can &lt;/sp=\r\nan&gt;happen. It is all about re-arranging karmas between the karmik pools. Ev=\r\nery action by one, or even people around one, has the &lt;span style=3D&quot;font-s=\r\ntyle:italic;&quot;&gt;potential &lt;/span&gt;to re-arrange one&#39;s karmik pools. A karma ab=\r\nout to give karmaphala may be postponed or a karma that was not to give kar=\r\nmaphala anytime soon may be advanced sooner.&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;However, =\r\nremember that the remedial measure has to be as intense as the karma that i=\r\nt is trying to manipulate. You can move a small rock with small force, but =\r\nyou need a large force to move a big rock or a hill.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;di=\r\nv&gt;If there is no negative karma in one&#39;s pool that can give a &lt;span style=\r\n=3D&quot;font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;specific &lt;/span&gt;result, nobody can make one experie=\r\nnce &lt;span style=3D&quot;font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;that &lt;/span&gt;result, no matter what r=\r\nitual one does. However, even great souls have a lot of negative karmas in =\r\ntheir optional pool and even evil people\n have a lot of positive karmas in =\r\ntheir optional pool, and hence powerful remedies, curses and blessings can =\r\noften make some difference.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;This point is well i=\r\nllustrated by the &quot;Guru Charitra&quot; story Digamber ji referred in his point (=\r\n3).&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; =\r\n*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;If=\r\n one thinks that one can escape the fruits of one&#39;s actions, one is mistake=\r\nned. God is not like us human beings, who may show favoritism towards those=\r\n who praise them or bribe them. The He-aspect of God is a witness to the pl=\r\nay of actions and fruits. The She-aspect of God is the power that impartial=\r\nly and impassionately manages the fine balance and order within this play o=\r\nf actions and fruits. All beings are equal in Her eyes, from the lowest of =\r\nevil persons to the noblest of saints. She administers just and balanced de=\r\nlivery of fruits to actions using\n available agents.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/=\r\ndiv&gt;The karmas we committed in the past are already in the pipeline and wil=\r\nl give their results sooner or later. The best we can do with them, with so=\r\nme effort, is to perhaps reorder them somewhat. The most important thing is=\r\n to not add more serious bad karmas to the pipeline &lt;span style=3D&quot;font-sty=\r\nle:italic;&quot;&gt;n&lt;span&gt;ow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; Simply put, selfish actio=\r\nns and actions that cause pain or harm to others are bad karmas and selfles=\r\ns actions and actions that cause pleasure or benefit to others are good kar=\r\nmas.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;When it comes to manipulating the pre-existing pipeline o=\r\nf karmas awaiting karmaphala, through conscious effort and current action, =\r\nyes, it is possible and general guidelines are available in shastras, but w=\r\ne can&#39;t be certain about the specific impact of each action. One thing is f=\r\nor sure - remedial measure for overcoming a karma has to be commensurate wi=\r\nth the karma\n itself.&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;You need only small force to push a cat =\r\nout of your way, but need a large force to push an elephant.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class=\r\n=3D&quot;yiv54243352yui_3_7_2_30_1362238784009_178&quot; style=3D&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);=\r\nfont-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-c=\r\nolor:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Best regards,&lt;br&gt;Narasimha&lt;b=\r\nr&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;Astrology &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; t=\r\narget=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a rel=3D&quot;nof=\r\nollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot;&gt;http://ww=\r\nw.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=3D&quot;yiv54243352yui_3_7_2_30_136223=\r\n8784009_179&quot; style=3D&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, =\r\nhelvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal=\r\n;&quot;&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;